Revision history for Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Prereqs-AuthorDeps

{{$NEXT}}

0.007     2020-05-17 11:41:40-04:00 America/New_York

    [CHANGED]

    - plugins that exist in the local build root are not added as prereqs.

0.006     2016-05-02 11:06:55-04:00 America/New_York

    [CHANGED]

    - Capped max Dist::Zilla prereq added to 5 until Dist::Zilla v6 is
      stable.

    [FIXES]

    - Drop vestigial use of Path::Class API to avoid Dist::Zilla 6
      deprecation warnings.

0.005     2015-08-11 11:39:40-04:00 America/New_York

    [FIXES]

    - Fixes failing test under Dist::Zilla 5.038 or later

0.004     2014-11-04 11:03:34-05:00 America/New_York

    [PREREQS]

    - Dropped Path::Class

    - Added more recent Dist::Zilla

0.003     2014-05-22 15:40:50-04:00 America/New_York

    [CHANGED]

    - Required Dist::Zilla version is now the integer portion only;
      plugins may require a later version, but this plugin now only
      mandates the last major release

    [TESTS]

    - Improved test coverage

0.002     2013-11-04 23:02:57 America/New_York

    [FIXED]

    - Fixed tests for old versions of Dist::Zilla

0.001     2013-11-04 21:04:57 America/New_York

    - First release

